            <def id="sexual-arousal" title="Sexual arousal">
                Sexual arousal describes the physiological and psychological responses in preparation for sexual
                intercourse or when exposed to sexual stimuli. A number of physiological responses occur in the body and
                mind as preparation for sexual intercourse, and continue during intercourse.
            </def>
